Save this as `.gitignore` in the same directory:

```gitignore
# Build artifacts
*.o
*.bin
*.elf
*.iso
*.img

# Build directories
/build/
isodir/boot/kernel.elf

# Logs and temporary files
*.log
*.tmp

# Editor and OS metadata
*.swp
*.swo
*.bak
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Backup files
*~

# Ignore compiled kernel outputs
kernel.map

# Exclude qemu output dumps
qemu_*.out